(13, '整理了一些Linux常用命令', 'uploads/20170602110407535.jpg', '<h3 style="font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; orphans: 2; white-space: normal; widows: 2; margin: 1.2em 0px 0.3em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(232, 71, 71);">常用指令</a></h3><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">ls &nbsp; &nbsp; 显示文件或目录</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; -l &nbsp;列出文件详细信息l(list)</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; -a &nbsp;列出当前目录下所有文件及目录，包括隐藏的a(all)</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">mkdir &nbsp;创建目录</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; -p &nbsp;创建目录，若无父目录，则创建p(parent) &nbsp;</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">cd &nbsp; &nbsp; 切换目录</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">touch &nbsp;创建空文件</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">echo &nbsp; 创建带有内容的文件。</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inheri