it; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">rm &nbsp; &nbsp; 删除文件</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; -r &nbsp;递归删除，可删除子目录及文件</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; -f &nbsp;强制删除</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">find &nbsp; 在文件系统中搜索某文件</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">wc &nbsp; &nbsp; 统计文本中行数、字数、字符数</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">grep &nbsp; 在文本文件中查找某个字符串</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">rmdir &nbsp;删除空目录</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">tree &nbsp; 树形结构显示目录，需要安装tree包</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">pwd &nbsp; &nbsp;显示当前目录</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(240, 240, 240); overflow: auto;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">ln &nbsp; &nbsp; 创建链接文件</span></code></p><p><code class="language-html" style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 1px 2px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: &quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;; vertical-ali